This was a perfect salad. Dressing couldn't be easier and its simplicity was a perfect complement to the rich flavors of the cheese and pecans. Used stilton and when you got a bit with all the ingredients together it was a party in your mouth. Super delicious - will definitely use this as a staple winter/spring salad.

