Made this for a dinner party and my guests raved about it! A keeper for sure. The combination of flavors was perfect. I made exactly as the recipe is written and it was wonderful. Easy substitutions would still result in a fabulous salad - blue cheese or gorgonzola, any type of pear as long as it is ripe and any mix of bitter greens, arugula!!

